Package com.brestats.model.data

Class Departement

java.lang.Object
com.brestats.model.data.Departement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Model
public class Departement extends Object implements Model
The Departement class represents a department with specific attributes such as its ID, name, and cultural investment for the year 2019. It implements the Model interface and provides methods to access and manipulate its data.

This class includes methods to get and set the department's ID, name, and cultural investment, as well as to return a string representation of the department.
